text: Nordkvaløya is an island in Norway. It is located north of Ringvassøya and west of Helgøya. The Norwegian Sea is northwest of it. The island is mountainous and covers an area of . The highest point is Storalangen at . In 2017, only three people lived on the island. == References == Category:Islands of Norway Category:Troms
